'''柯迪‧艾德華‧艾倫''' {{BD|1988年|11月20日||}} 為美國大聯盟(MLB)職棒後援投手, 生涯曾效力過印地安人與天使等隊。

==學生時期==
艾倫在[[奧蘭多,_佛羅里達|奧蘭多, 佛羅里達]]高中時期於威廉.布恩高中打球，大學時期於中央佛羅里達大學與聖彼得堡大學。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/sports/baseball/os-world-series-cleveland-indians-cody-allen-20161024-story.html|title=With World Series on tap, Orlando native thrives as Cleveland Indians' closer|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=|archive-date=2019-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418163540/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/sports/baseball/os-world-series-cleveland-indians-cody-allen-20161024-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2011年美國大聯盟選秀時期, 他在第23順位被克里夫蘭印地安人隊指定。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120720&content_id=35254170&notebook_id=35256138&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle|title=Allen throws scoreless frame in debut|publisher=Major League Baseball Advanced Media|accessdate=29 September 2012|date=21 July 2012|last=Meisel|first=Zack|work=[[Mlb.com|Mlb.com]]|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115210/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120720&content_id=35254170&notebook_id=35256138&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle|dead-url=no}}</ref>
接下來該年成為小聯盟球員磨練後才成功進入大聯盟。<ref name="Panthers">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=592102|accessdate=29 September 2012|publisher=Major League Baseball Advanced Media|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|title=Cody Allen Stats, Video Highlights, Photos, Bio|archive-date=2015-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404035746/http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=592102|dead-url=no}}</ref>

艾倫在2011年時於印地安人隊農場系統轉換了四個球隊, 但主要大部分時間在[[馬洪寧河谷拳師狗隊|馬洪寧河谷拳師狗隊]], 在14場比在中取得3勝1敗/防禦率2.14的成績。
接著在[[哥倫布快艇隊|哥倫布快艇隊]], 在24場比在中取得3勝2敗/防禦率2.27的成績。並於該球季結束後, 被印地安人隊由投手身分登入大聯盟名單中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20121205&content_id=40534634&vkey=pr_cle&c_id=cle |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-03 |archive-date=2014-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326180406/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20121205&content_id=40534634&vkey=pr_cle&c_id=cle |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==職業時期==
2012年7月20日, 艾倫終於首次登場就在[[Triple-A_(baseball)|3A]] [[哥倫布快艇隊|哥倫布快艇隊]]上來後, <ref>{{cite news|url=http://highpointpanthers.com/news/2012/7/20/Baseball_0720124152.aspx?path=baseball|title=Cody Allen promoted to the Cleveland Indians|accessdate=29 September 2012|date=20 July 2012|work=Highpointpanthers.com|archive-date=2019-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113210243/https://highpointpanthers.com/news/2012/7/20/Baseball_0720124152.aspx?path=baseball|dead-url=no}}</ref>
並且成功投出救援任務,無上壘、無安打, 1次三振。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/news/thome-hits-homer-no-610-022414763--mlb.html|title=Thome hits homer No. 610, Orioles top Indians 10-2|work=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]]|agency=Associated Press|date=20 July 2012|accessdate=29 September 2012|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104021821/http://sports.yahoo.com/news/thome-hits-homer-no-610-022414763--mlb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[巴爾的摩金鶯隊|巴爾的摩金鶯隊]]三壘手[[Mark_Reynolds|Mark Reynolds]]成為了他職業生涯首次三振苦主。<br />
2013年, 艾倫達成6勝1負/防禦率2.43/三振數88的好成績, 他的77場救援在美聯季賽中僅次於[[Joel_Peralta|Joel Peralta]]的80場。<br />
在2014年季初, 當家終結者[[John_Axford|John Axford]]投得非常掙扎, 於是該年五月艾倫開始分擔任終結者的腳色。最後季賽結束, 總共出賽76場, 在69.2局中取得6勝4負/防禦率2.07/91三振/24救援成功的成績。<br />
2015年，艾倫出賽70場, 在69又1/3局中取得34場救援成功/99次三振/防禦率2.99。

2021年2月17日，艾倫宣布正式退休。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.letsgotribe.com/2021/2/17/22287276/former-cleveland-closer-cody-allen-is-retiring |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-18 |archive-date=2021-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217151631/https://www.letsgotribe.com/2021/2/17/22287276/former-cleveland-closer-cody-allen-is-retiring |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/02/cody-allen-retires.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-18 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222013830/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/02/cody-allen-retires.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
